========================================
Under The Sea - Vietnamese NLP Toolkit
========================================


.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/underthesea.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/underthesea

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/underthesea.svg
